snippet: The asset manager said it had received a Wells notice from the regulator over potential trading infractions concerning an exchange-traded fund in 2012.
abstract: DealBook Online; Pimco reports that Securities and Exchange Commission may file action over potential trading infractions of its Pimco Total Return ETF bond fund.

headline.main: Pimco May Face S.E.C. Action Over a Fund
